HISTOGRAM - displays the frequency or count of values in the specified column

In [7]:
sns.histplot(x='total',data=df)
plt.title("HIstogram of total car crashes")
plt.show()

Pairplot - For exploring relationship between numerical columns

In [8]:
sns.pairplot(df)
plt.show()

Boxplot - for visualizing the distributions and outliers

In [9]:

In [10]:
